## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="fc753-102">通常情况下，当从 Windows 窗体应用程序打印时，你创建的新实例<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>类中，设置属性，如<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A>并<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A>，用于描述如何打印和调用<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A>方法来实际打印文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-102">Typically, when you print from a Windows Forms application, you create a new instance of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> class, set properties, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.DefaultPageSettings%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A>, that describe how to print, and call the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A> method to actually print the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-103">调用<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法将引发<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件，应处理来执行打印文档的布局。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-103">Calling the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method raises the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=nameWithType> event, which should be handled to perform the document layout for printing.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="fc753-104">使用<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.Graphics%2A>的属性<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs>对象，来自<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件，以指定要打印的输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-104">Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.Graphics%2A> property of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs> object obtained from the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=nameWithType> event to specify the output to print.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-105">如果要打印的文本文件，使用<xref:System.IO.StreamReader>以便从流，并调用一次读取一行<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawString%2A>方法来绘制图形对象中的行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-105">If you are printing a text file, use <xref:System.IO.StreamReader> to read one line at a time from the stream and call the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawString%2A> method to draw the line in the graphics object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-106">有关此过程的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>和<xref:System.IO.StreamReader>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-106">For more information about this process, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> and <xref:System.IO.StreamReader> classes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-107">您可以查看打印文本文档中的示例<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>类概述主题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-107">You can view an example of printing a text document in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> class overview topic.</span></span>  
  
