 <span data-ttu-id="fc753-110">在派生类中实现时<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController>控件如何<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>打印。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-110">When implemented in a derived class, the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController> controls how a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> is printed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-111"><xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法将调用打印控制器<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>， <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnEndPrint%2A>， <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnStartPage%2A>，和<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnEndPage%2A>方法指示打印机如何打印文档的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-111">The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method invokes the print controller's <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnEndPrint%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnStartPage%2A>, and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController.OnEndPage%2A> methods, which in turn tell the printer how to print the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fc753-112">有关打印对话框的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fc753-112">For more information about printing dialog boxes, see <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog>.</span></span>  
  
